import React from 'react';
import {
  Box,
  Typography,
  Paper,
  List,
  ListItem,
  ListItemText,
  Switch,
  Divider,
  FormControlLabel,
} from '@mui/material';

const Settings = () => {
  return (
    <Paper sx={{ p: 3, height: '100%' }}>
      <Typography variant="h4" gutterBottom>
        Settings
      </Typography>
      <Typography variant="body1" color="text.secondary" paragraph>
        Customize your experience by adjusting these settings.
      </Typography>
      <List>
        <ListItem>
          <ListItemText 
            primary="Dark Mode" 
            secondary="Toggle between light and dark theme"
          />
          <FormControlLabel
            control={<Switch />}
            label=""
          />
        </ListItem>
        <Divider />
        <ListItem>
          <ListItemText 
            primary="Notifications" 
            secondary="Enable or disable notifications"
          />
          <FormControlLabel
            control={<Switch />}
            label=""
          />
        </ListItem>
        <Divider />
        <ListItem>
          <ListItemText 
            primary="Auto-save" 
            secondary="Automatically save your work"
          />
          <FormControlLabel
            control={<Switch />}
            label=""
          />
        </ListItem>
      </List>
    </Paper>
  );
};

export default Settings;
